{"tid":1748523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Be humble] 各位手足，對住同路人可唔可以客氣少少？","createTime":"2019-11-23T17:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T05:20:13.000Z","uid":54778,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"29c9bcab0d82ce60d64337adaf97d711fc59fed7","tid":1748523,"uid":54778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T17:12:08.000Z","msg":"話說有日行過葵涌邨附近，有個黑口罩嘅人（唔知係咪手足喇）迎面行過嚟，我都盡量讓一讓俾佢行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢一嘢撞埋嚟，仲要頭也不回咁走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加上最近發夢嘅經歷，有啲嘢真係好想同大家講<br />\n<br />\n我明白過咗咁耐，有咁多事發生，總不免有啲情緒嘅...但唔該各位請記得：<br />\n發夢蒙面係為咗保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日常戴口罩，係為咗表達對禁蒙面法嘅不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而唔係為咗任意妄為、任意屌人</span></span><br />\n<br />\nBe humble 呢樣嘢講咗好耐<br />\n但係到今時今日，發夢嗰陣我都仲見到有手足係會對街坊/路人破口大罵，明明佢地係乜都冇做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至有時對住手足，都係用呼呼喝喝嘅態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足做錯少少，都俾人大大聲咁屌<br />\n<br />\n可能你會話，咁多個月，少少嘢都做錯係抵屌。但係點解咁多個月，都仲未學識be humble?<br />\n<br />\n仲有，你覺得心情差，唔該自己處理好。揾街邊嘅人同手足發洩有咩意思？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你咁樣，同隨機搞街坊出氣嘅黑警有咩分別？</span></span>你咁樣揾自己人嚟出氣，你估佢地又會好開心？咁樣只會令到士氣更低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗平日都俾人罵啦...發夢幫手又要俾人罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你話我EQ低又好，抗壓能力低又好<br />\n我唔係要求大家彬彬有禮，只係對自己人可以客氣返少少，至少雙方都唔會有hard feeling，又唔會影響士氣，對大家都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後希望各位做一個有質素嘅發夢師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而唔係一個成日嬲爆爆、起晒鋼嘅憤青。<br />\n<br />\n記得早啲瞓，聽日去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ded299fa38563e322454b42bd7e64b7d95607b","tid":1748523,"uid":135390,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T17:17:41.000Z","msg":"葵涌邨有狗竇 所以戴口罩未必係手足"},{"pid":"2259e7c9dfda82fcc78c0745ada0088d72eedcaa","tid":1748523,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T17:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGDp2wW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGDp2wW.jpg&h=f4218c79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1397cf847586527862375eab4311e104e91e916","tid":1748523,"uid":241108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T17:20:48.000Z","msg":"耩得好"},{"pid":"a1033f665483f1c5a13f59a947093f827f1bd0c2","tid":1748523,"uid":54778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:59:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n記得投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00ee950a4f340e19ecd04829822c177762d96e7","tid":1748523,"uid":54778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4600e9532a59a90c204d2d191aacbf597e342dda","tid":1748523,"uid":54778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:21:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de0d32246915b1bf4005058109197e7def32faf6","tid":1748523,"uid":54778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:16:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2cdd5dc907014c4cc3acd7aba2952c6975e91063","tid":1748523,"uid":8550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4319ed7d2b4520696ad88543ea9e3b5d0721df","tid":1748523,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:42:32.000Z","msg":"嗰D有出過遊行，但唔出去投票想點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfa250afa7d40c10cf279345d01fbf76ae00d1c","tid":1748523,"uid":54778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd4319ed7d2b4520696ad88543ea9e3b5d0721df","t